1
00:00:35,620 --> 00:00:38,780
Mast! Lay down the mast!

2
00:00:44,660 --> 00:00:46,340
Hurry up and get the rope!

3
00:00:47,660 --> 00:00:50,340
Bow and stern face the banks! Quick!

4
00:00:54,020 --> 00:00:56,420
Thousands of homes are brightly lit,

5
00:00:56,420 --> 00:00:58,860
and the doors to them are wide open.

6
00:00:58,860 --> 00:01:01,020
This is East Capital.

7
00:01:01,620 --> 00:01:04,620
New wine at Sunyang Restaurant!

8
00:01:04,620 --> 00:01:07,140
Welcome to enjoy it!

9
00:01:07,300 --> 00:01:09,820
​If you want to know what happens next,

10
00:01:09,820 --> 00:01:11,900
wait until next time.

11
00:01:12,140 --> 00:01:14,420
People from all over the world gather here,

12
00:01:14,420 --> 00:01:17,380
and envoys from various countries come to communicate with the authorities.

13
00:01:22,660 --> 00:01:24,660
[Riverside Code at Qingming Festival]

14
00:01:24,660 --> 00:01:26,660
[Adapted from Ye Wenbiao's Novel Series of the Same Name]

15
00:01:27,180 --> 00:01:27,980
[Episode 7]

16
00:01:27,980 --> 00:01:28,680
[Observation is not done by eyes.]

17
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:29,180
[Not with your eyes, but with your heart.]

18
00:01:29,180 --> 00:01:29,980
[Not with your heart, but with senses. - by Shao Yong, Northern Song]

19
00:01:30,460 --> 00:01:31,120
[Yanglou Street, East Capital]

20
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:31,870
Sun Bo,

21
00:01:32,360 --> 00:01:34,230
Someone testified

22
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:35,870
that you had a conflict

23
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:38,310
with Wu Xiang in Wu's Restaurant.

24
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:39,720
Sir,

25
00:01:40,310 --> 00:01:42,080
I just had a little altercation

26
00:01:42,270 --> 00:01:43,510
with Wu Xiang.

27
00:01:44,440 --> 00:01:45,590
Is the witness here?

28
00:01:46,160 --> 00:01:46,760
Yes!

29
00:01:47,400 --> 00:01:48,000
Look.

30
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:50,800
Check if it was him.

31
00:01:52,360 --> 00:01:53,270
Sir,

32
00:01:53,270 --> 00:01:55,310
My home is diagonal to the Wus.

33
00:01:55,310 --> 00:01:57,480
I happened to have left home

34
00:01:57,480 --> 00:01:58,830
before the hour of Zi last night.

35
00:01:58,830 --> 00:01:59,910
I saw someone

36
00:01:59,910 --> 00:02:01,800
sneaking into the Wus.

37
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:05,800
It was him!

38
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:07,950
He really is the guy.

39
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:10,600
You can never judge a book by its cover.

40
00:02:11,630 --> 00:02:13,270
What were you doing at their home so late?

41
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:17,080
I was here to pay my debt.

42
00:02:17,080 --> 00:02:18,960
Who pays debt at such a late hour?

43
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:21,910
I'm working all day long to earn money.

44
00:02:21,910 --> 00:02:23,360
Nonsense!

45
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:26,030
He was alive when you got there,

46
00:02:26,190 --> 00:02:27,960
and he died after you left.

47
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:28,800
What kind of debt did you pay?

48
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:30,390
The kind that takes one's life?

49
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:33,110
It's the Hat Demon!

50
00:02:33,910 --> 00:02:34,750
It's the Hat Demon!

51
00:02:35,440 --> 00:02:36,270
We saw it

52
00:02:36,270 --> 00:02:37,470
sucking a human soul,

53
00:02:37,720 --> 00:02:38,440
and it can fly.

54
00:02:38,440 --> 00:02:39,320
The audacity!

55
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:44,600
This is just like the rumor from five years ago.

56
00:02:45,080 --> 00:02:46,390
Inspector Gu and I

57
00:02:46,390 --> 00:02:48,670
investigated countless

58
00:02:48,670 --> 00:02:49,630
murder cases.

59
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:52,160
With him looking over the neighbor,

60
00:02:52,750 --> 00:02:54,440
no demon dares to run riot.

61
00:02:54,440 --> 00:02:55,160
Yes!

62
00:02:55,160 --> 00:02:56,190
It dares not!

63
00:02:56,750 --> 00:02:58,750
Sun Bo, the errand boy,

64
00:02:59,910 --> 00:03:02,000
is busy working all day long.

65
00:03:02,270 --> 00:03:03,880
The scarce money he made

66
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:06,080
was exploited by Wu Xiang.

67
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:08,390
So, he faked the Hat Demon

68
00:03:08,750 --> 00:03:09,880
and got back at Wu Xiang in his home.

69
00:03:09,880 --> 00:03:11,160
Do you confess?

70
00:03:11,550 --> 00:03:12,270
Sir…

71
00:03:12,270 --> 00:03:13,240
See?

72
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:15,080
He's not arguing. So, he acquiesced in my accusation.

73
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:15,720
Guards!

74
00:03:15,720 --> 00:03:16,600
Yes!

75
00:03:16,600 --> 00:03:17,440
Arrest him!

76
00:03:17,440 --> 00:03:18,270
Yes.

77
00:03:18,550 --> 00:03:19,270
Judge Wan,

78
00:03:19,670 --> 00:03:20,720
all you've said

79
00:03:21,030 --> 00:03:22,160
is just your guess.

80
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:23,650
Mo'er！

81
00:03:24,160 --> 00:03:25,390
You have no evidence.

82
00:03:25,390 --> 00:03:26,440
On what base are you arresting him?

83
00:03:26,880 --> 00:03:27,390
Who's that?

84
00:03:27,750 --> 00:03:28,600
You! Come here.

85
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,750
Is this what you call an investigation?

86
00:03:32,190 --> 00:03:33,240
You haven't done the autopsy

87
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:34,550
or investigate the crime scene.

88
00:03:35,270 --> 00:03:36,910
I was there for Bo

89
00:03:36,910 --> 00:03:37,750
and Wu Xiang's spat.

90
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:39,630
It was just a small conflict.

91
00:03:39,880 --> 00:03:41,440
How could it possibly lead to revenge by killing?

92
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:43,520
The motive you claimed

93
00:03:43,880 --> 00:03:45,030
doesn't make sense.

94
00:03:49,440 --> 00:03:50,360
Young man,

95
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:54,110
you need to learn to think

96
00:03:55,550 --> 00:03:56,390
before act.

97
00:03:59,830 --> 00:04:01,030
One more word

98
00:04:01,030 --> 00:04:03,000
and I'll send misery upon your brother.

99
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:04,880
You haven't thought about that, have you?

100
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:08,630
How dare the Hat Demon come out under such broad daylight?

101
00:04:09,160 --> 00:04:12,270
It must be some treacherous man trying to disturb our peaceful life!

102
00:04:13,550 --> 00:04:14,190
Fei Jian!

103
00:04:14,390 --> 00:04:14,910
Yes!

104
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:15,630
Get him.

105
00:04:15,630 --> 00:04:16,070
Yes.

106
00:04:17,690 --> 00:04:18,420
Move!

107
00:04:20,950 --> 00:04:21,510
Move aside!

108
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,240
Move aside!

109
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:38,440
Let's head back.

110
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:39,230
Yes.

111
00:04:39,510 --> 00:04:40,070
Move aside!

112
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:42,270
- Clear the path. - Why does the Hat Demon visit Yanglou Street so often?

113
00:04:42,670 --> 00:04:44,440
They have the killer there.

114
00:04:44,440 --> 00:04:45,200
It's not the Hat Demon.

115
00:04:46,550 --> 00:04:48,040
Well, I'm not staying here.

116
00:04:48,670 --> 00:04:49,720
Pity. It is a superior area.

117
00:04:50,070 --> 00:04:51,480
It's so close to the royal garden.

118
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:55,480
I heard that it belongs to Zhang Qiniang.

119
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:56,760
The property agent said

120
00:04:56,760 --> 00:04:58,230
that if this keeps up,

121
00:04:58,230 --> 00:04:59,270
the price of the properties here will drop.

122
00:05:01,510 --> 00:05:02,760
It's not like I can fly out of here, Mo'er.

123
00:05:02,760 --> 00:05:03,600
Untie me.

124
00:05:03,670 --> 00:05:04,790
This is undignified.

125
00:05:05,070 --> 00:05:05,760
Wait.

126
00:05:06,440 --> 00:05:08,390
Sun Bo must have been wronged.

127
00:05:08,390 --> 00:05:09,830
Just let me take a look.

128
00:05:10,270 --> 00:05:12,390
Mo'er, that's the autopsy room.

129
00:05:12,390 --> 00:05:14,550
I'm just a coroner, what can I do?

130
00:05:16,080 --> 00:05:16,900
How about this?

131
00:05:17,230 --> 00:05:18,160
You come with me.

132
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:19,230
I'll watch while you do the autopsy.

133
00:05:19,230 --> 00:05:20,040
I won't meddle.

134
00:05:21,110 --> 00:05:22,760
Mo'er, please stop giving me such a hard time.

135
00:05:23,390 --> 00:05:24,720
I'll level with you.

136
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:26,950
The man had such a horrible death

137
00:05:26,950 --> 00:05:28,440
and I haven't had the nerve to look.

138
00:05:29,320 --> 00:05:32,720
I'm going to ask my father to work on this case.

139
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:34,200
He has so many rules

140
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:35,550
and he'll never let you in.

141
00:05:36,320 --> 00:05:37,640
You don't have the nerve to look.

142
00:05:37,760 --> 00:05:39,040
So, in the Mei's Boat Case…

143
00:05:39,390 --> 00:05:40,790
If it weren't for Zhao Ban'er,

144
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:42,550
I'd have been expelled.

145
00:05:47,950 --> 00:05:49,080
What's your problem?

146
00:05:51,270 --> 00:05:52,350
Physician Ge.

147
00:05:53,790 --> 00:05:56,350
I feel depressed.

148
00:05:58,390 --> 00:06:01,000
If you won't let me be your student,

149
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:03,110
I can help with the chores here.

150
00:06:03,510 --> 00:06:05,790
My sister-in-law made the cured meat.

151
00:06:06,350 --> 00:06:07,230
Try it.

152
00:06:09,670 --> 00:06:10,420
Get up.

153
00:06:10,420 --> 00:06:11,320
Get up and we will talk.

154
00:06:13,320 --> 00:06:14,720
Didn't you get

155
00:06:15,670 --> 00:06:17,880
what I said the last time?

156
00:06:18,110 --> 00:06:19,390
You have no chance.

157
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:21,640
I already have a new student.

158
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:23,950
Hey, come here.

159
00:06:26,830 --> 00:06:28,000
Listen up.

160
00:06:28,640 --> 00:06:31,390
If you let her in again,

161
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:33,200
you will be the one leaving.

162
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:34,760
Do you get it?

163
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:35,440
Yes, Master.

164
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:36,440
Go about your business.

165
00:06:36,840 --> 00:06:37,660
- Get out! - Wait.

166
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:38,970
Physician Ge.

167
00:06:39,200 --> 00:06:40,160
- Out! - Please help me.

168
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:42,040
- I really want to be a physician. - Go!

169
00:07:01,550 --> 00:07:02,920
Remember,

170
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:04,040
her name is Zhao Ban'er,

171
00:07:05,070 --> 00:07:06,510
and she's my sister.

172
00:07:07,350 --> 00:07:08,920
I'm the only one who can bully her.

173
00:07:09,510 --> 00:07:10,640
You don't have the right.

174
00:07:15,790 --> 00:07:16,880
Pick up the cured meat.

175
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:23,320
If they don't want you here,

176
00:07:23,320 --> 00:07:24,880
then we don't want them.

177
00:07:27,070 --> 00:07:28,230
Time is of the essence.

178
00:07:28,330 --> 00:07:28,940
Let's go.

179
00:07:28,940 --> 00:07:32,900
[Residence of Imperial Physician Zhao]

180
00:07:33,220 --> 00:07:34,660
[Autopsy Room of the Kaifeng Prefecture]

181
00:07:40,230 --> 00:07:42,280
This is all about you needing my help.

182
00:07:42,880 --> 00:07:43,790
Sun Bo is in trouble.

183
00:07:44,200 --> 00:07:44,920
I suppose

184
00:07:45,070 --> 00:07:46,550
you will not stand by and watch, right?

185
00:07:47,200 --> 00:07:47,880
Yeah.

186
00:07:48,350 --> 00:07:50,070
Inspector Gu allowed you

187
00:07:50,070 --> 00:07:51,320
to help me out once.

188
00:07:53,270 --> 00:07:54,040
I'll try.

189
00:07:54,550 --> 00:07:55,950
The deceased, Wu Xiang,

190
00:07:56,290 --> 00:07:57,550
the first son of the Wus.

191
00:07:57,550 --> 00:07:58,720
34 years old.

192
00:07:59,440 --> 00:08:00,320
Turn around.

193
00:08:00,790 --> 00:08:02,270
The Wus run the Wu's Restaurant.

194
00:08:02,270 --> 00:08:03,390
His younger brother, Wu Ao,

195
00:08:03,640 --> 00:08:04,880
is a student preparing for the imperial examinations.

196
00:08:05,440 --> 00:08:06,640
Their younger sister, Wu Qiao…

197
00:08:06,640 --> 00:08:07,350
Spread your fingers.

198
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:08,760
…is the chef in the house.

199
00:08:08,790 --> 00:08:09,880
She has a severe leg problem

200
00:08:10,390 --> 00:08:11,160
that she can't walk.

201
00:08:11,790 --> 00:08:13,040
So, what's the first step?

202
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:14,880
Check for injuries.

203
00:08:23,950 --> 00:08:24,670
There is none.

204
00:08:24,880 --> 00:08:26,160
Check his limbs

205
00:08:26,320 --> 00:08:27,760
for any

206
00:08:28,110 --> 00:08:29,180
broken bones.

207
00:08:35,400 --> 00:08:36,760
Nothing.

208
00:08:38,400 --> 00:08:40,200
Could it really be the Hat Demon?

209
00:08:43,710 --> 00:08:45,350
Is there any other possible cause of death?

210
00:08:45,910 --> 00:08:46,670
Poison?

211
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:49,350
Some poisons cannot be identified from observation.

212
00:08:49,350 --> 00:08:50,440
We can try that.

213
00:08:50,760 --> 00:08:51,670
I'm familiar with that.

214
00:08:52,110 --> 00:08:52,640
I'll do it.

215
00:08:53,470 --> 00:08:54,180
I'll help.

216
00:08:54,180 --> 00:08:54,760
All right.

217
00:08:55,760 --> 00:08:57,760
Black locust water and forceps.

218
00:08:59,790 --> 00:09:02,230
Clean the silver plate with black locust water

219
00:09:02,590 --> 00:09:03,790
and put it in the mouth of the deceased.

220
00:09:04,550 --> 00:09:07,030
We'll know if the poison was oral.

221
00:09:12,640 --> 00:09:13,200
It's done.

222
00:09:13,470 --> 00:09:14,110
Is it?

223
00:09:14,230 --> 00:09:14,880
Yes.

224
00:09:16,550 --> 00:09:17,280
Yao He,

225
00:09:17,280 --> 00:09:18,710
how long do we have to wait?

226
00:09:19,030 --> 00:09:19,760
Four hours.

227
00:09:19,760 --> 00:09:22,030
Four hours! That's really long.

228
00:09:24,400 --> 00:09:25,640
Are you trying to cut the body open again?

229
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:27,150
You didn't let me do it the last time.

230
00:09:27,150 --> 00:09:28,150
We can't wait that long this time.

231
00:09:39,150 --> 00:09:40,790
What does his bowels look like?

232
00:09:41,520 --> 00:09:42,960
It's full of twists and turns.

233
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:44,880
Then you'll see a bulk of something.

234
00:09:45,280 --> 00:09:46,280
That should be it.

235
00:09:55,030 --> 00:09:55,710
I've got it.

236
00:10:00,150 --> 00:10:00,960
Test it now!

237
00:10:01,710 --> 00:10:03,230
Pass me a silver plate from my drawer.

238
00:10:03,320 --> 00:10:04,200
Silver plate…

239
00:10:10,640 --> 00:10:11,470
Is there no poison?

240
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:13,080
No.

241
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:14,760
No poison.

242
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:17,760
This is normal.

243
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:21,230
There are countless poisons in the world.

244
00:10:21,230 --> 00:10:22,550
You can't identify all of them

245
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:23,760
with silver.

246
00:10:24,400 --> 00:10:25,670
What should we do now?

247
00:10:29,110 --> 00:10:30,350
I have a solution.

248
00:10:31,280 --> 00:10:33,400
If we can find a rat or a sparrow,

249
00:10:33,710 --> 00:10:34,960
I can test the poison on living things.

250
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:36,320
Feed them some of this

251
00:10:37,030 --> 00:10:38,150
and we'll know.

252
00:10:38,150 --> 00:10:39,000
Living things.

253
00:10:40,080 --> 00:10:40,880
Well,

254
00:10:41,470 --> 00:10:42,470
there's a chicken in the yard.

255
00:10:42,550 --> 00:10:43,280
Ban'er, let's go.

256
00:10:44,500 --> 00:10:45,240
No, Ban'er!

257
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:47,000
I'm using that to make you furnace-roasted chicken.

258
00:10:53,380 --> 00:10:54,280
[Mr. Huang, Litigation Guild]

259
00:10:54,280 --> 00:10:55,080
Mr. Huang,

260
00:10:55,520 --> 00:10:57,910
I heard that you like the Lotus Fish.

261
00:10:58,110 --> 00:11:00,200
I made it myself. Try it.

262
00:11:00,400 --> 00:11:02,350
Where did you find the lotus seedpod?

263
00:11:02,520 --> 00:11:05,590
The lotus seedpods we usually see are tough and hard.

264
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:08,400
Mine is different.

265
00:11:08,520 --> 00:11:09,590
Please have a try.

266
00:11:10,710 --> 00:11:11,590
Let me try it.

267
00:11:17,550 --> 00:11:19,230
It's made of flour!

268
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:21,030
It goes easy on my teeth.

269
00:11:22,030 --> 00:11:23,350
If you like it,

270
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:26,200
I'll ask my husband to deliver some from time to time.

271
00:11:27,350 --> 00:11:29,080
People in the neighborhood say

272
00:11:29,080 --> 00:11:31,710
that Mr. Huang tends to help newcomers.

273
00:11:32,110 --> 00:11:33,520
My husband just got started.

274
00:11:33,590 --> 00:11:34,840
We hope to get some advice from you.

275
00:11:39,550 --> 00:11:41,440
You are a junior official

276
00:11:41,710 --> 00:11:43,150
and it's not easy for you to change your profession.

277
00:11:43,640 --> 00:11:46,000
We will not charge you for membership.

278
00:11:46,280 --> 00:11:48,840
Just get a litigation book

279
00:11:49,320 --> 00:11:50,200
and study.

280
00:11:50,840 --> 00:11:51,640
Thank you, Mr. Huang.

281
00:11:52,440 --> 00:11:53,790
I've read

282
00:11:53,790 --> 00:11:55,400
all the litigation books.

283
00:11:55,400 --> 00:11:56,470
I know them like the back of my hand.

284
00:11:58,150 --> 00:11:59,640
Then don't do it.

285
00:11:59,640 --> 00:12:01,080
We will.

286
00:12:01,640 --> 00:12:02,880
Where can we get one?

287
00:12:06,030 --> 00:12:07,110
[Deng Sixian]
50 guan.

288
00:12:08,030 --> 00:12:09,080
[Deng Sixian]
100 guan.

289
00:12:09,710 --> 00:12:10,880
[Deng Sixian]
200 guan.

290
00:12:10,880 --> 00:12:11,760
Which one do you want?

291
00:12:12,840 --> 00:12:15,150
These three are identical.

292
00:12:15,150 --> 00:12:16,150
It is clarified in the guild rules

293
00:12:16,150 --> 00:12:17,710
that the location of each litigation booth or shop

294
00:12:17,710 --> 00:12:19,030
will be designated by the guild.

295
00:12:19,520 --> 00:12:21,520
The 200-guan one

296
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:24,150
gets you a location near the Kaifeng Prefecture.

297
00:12:24,200 --> 00:12:25,790
There are always cases there,

298
00:12:25,790 --> 00:12:26,640
which means booming business.

299
00:12:27,790 --> 00:12:29,280
The 100-guan one

300
00:12:29,640 --> 00:12:32,030
gets you a location near the Office of Justice.

301
00:12:33,470 --> 00:12:35,710
You know that place well.

302
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:40,320
And this one?

303
00:12:41,440 --> 00:12:42,200
Wen Yue.

304
00:12:42,440 --> 00:12:43,760
That one still costs 50 guan.

305
00:12:44,880 --> 00:12:45,640
Let me see.

306
00:12:46,150 --> 00:12:47,960
A spot is about to open on Xiangran Street.

307
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:48,790
Do you want it?

308
00:12:49,280 --> 00:12:50,030
- Yes. - No way!

309
00:12:50,030 --> 00:12:50,960
We will get the spot.

310
00:12:51,470 --> 00:12:52,230
Give me the money.

311
00:12:53,350 --> 00:12:54,080
Wen Yue.

312
00:12:54,400 --> 00:12:55,880
- 50 guan is too expensive. - Hurry up!

313
00:13:00,760 --> 00:13:02,150
Then we'll get this one.

314
00:13:06,760 --> 00:13:08,000
This is extortion!

315
00:13:08,470 --> 00:13:10,080
I haven't earned any money

316
00:13:10,840 --> 00:13:12,320
and have already lost 50 guan.

317
00:13:13,080 --> 00:13:14,470
We will earn money over time

318
00:13:14,470 --> 00:13:15,640
and get the fee back.

319
00:13:15,960 --> 00:13:18,470
We have a new way of living, at least.

320
00:13:18,760 --> 00:13:19,470
Let's go.

321
00:13:19,710 --> 00:13:20,910
I'll go check the spot on Xiangran Street with you.

322
00:13:21,470 --> 00:13:23,440
It's okay. It's just some unhygienic food.

323
00:13:23,550 --> 00:13:25,520
I'll get you some nice food later.

324
00:13:28,030 --> 00:13:29,640
The chicken is all right.

325
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:31,760
That means there's no poison.

326
00:13:34,470 --> 00:13:35,550
Could it

327
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:37,280
be the Hat Demon who did it?

328
00:13:37,640 --> 00:13:38,790
Do you believe in that?

329
00:13:38,790 --> 00:13:40,000
No, of course.

330
00:13:42,080 --> 00:13:43,080
Me neither.

331
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:45,000
But…

332
00:13:45,440 --> 00:13:46,530
It was sucking human soul

333
00:13:46,530 --> 00:13:47,960
and then the Hat Demon started to fly.

334
00:13:47,960 --> 00:13:49,230
How do you explain that?

335
00:13:49,840 --> 00:13:51,400
We need to check the crime scene.

336
00:13:53,470 --> 00:13:55,880
The Kaifeng Prefecture is guarding the place.

337
00:13:55,880 --> 00:13:56,590
We can't get in.

338
00:13:56,590 --> 00:13:57,670
Not during the day.

339
00:13:58,230 --> 00:13:59,670
We'll sneak in at night.

340
00:14:00,780 --> 00:14:01,260
[Litigation]

341
00:14:03,200 --> 00:14:04,000
Wen Yue.

342
00:14:04,000 --> 00:14:05,960
Best litigation booth in the capital city

343
00:14:06,110 --> 00:14:07,350
is now in business.

344
00:14:09,440 --> 00:14:11,520
Is this what you meant

345
00:14:12,520 --> 00:14:14,230
by setting up the litigation booth?

346
00:14:14,710 --> 00:14:16,590
Litigator is about capability.

347
00:14:17,550 --> 00:14:18,910
I don't need anything fancy.

348
00:14:21,200 --> 00:14:22,030
What do you think?

349
00:14:22,710 --> 00:14:23,550
Zhao Buyou.

350
00:14:24,230 --> 00:14:25,790
I didn't want to point out the elephant in the room.

351
00:14:26,110 --> 00:14:27,790
How could you pretend to be sick yesterday

352
00:14:27,790 --> 00:14:29,150
when something so important happened?

353
00:14:30,590 --> 00:14:32,550
Where have you been for the last few days?

354
00:14:32,590 --> 00:14:33,960
I was feeling bad.

355
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:38,790
Wen Yue, where are you going?

356
00:14:38,840 --> 00:14:40,110
Back to the umbrella shop.

357
00:14:41,840 --> 00:14:43,760
Get yourself checked by Physician Ge

358
00:14:43,760 --> 00:14:45,400
after you close the booth today.

359
00:14:45,590 --> 00:14:47,030
It's time to talk to him

360
00:14:47,030 --> 00:14:48,000
about Ban'er again.

361
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:48,790
Yes.

362
00:14:50,710 --> 00:14:52,350
You are not feeling well, right?

363
00:14:52,440 --> 00:14:53,440
Get some treatment.

364
00:14:54,520 --> 00:14:55,400
You can count on me.

365
00:14:56,030 --> 00:14:56,710
I will finish the task.

366
00:15:04,340 --> 00:15:07,660
[Waiting for Business, Day Two]

367
00:15:07,790 --> 00:15:08,710
Tonight,

368
00:15:08,710 --> 00:15:11,670
Lady Zhang will be at the Yanglou Street in person

369
00:15:11,790 --> 00:15:13,080
for the demon-hunting bounty.

370
00:15:13,320 --> 00:15:15,910
[Demon Hunting Bounty]
Whoever catches the Hat Demon gets

371
00:15:16,280 --> 00:15:17,230
500 guan.

372
00:15:17,880 --> 00:15:18,840
500 guan!

373
00:15:19,030 --> 00:15:19,710
That's a lot!

374
00:15:20,840 --> 00:15:22,200
[Death to the Hat Demon]
These are all people with special talents.

375
00:15:22,680 --> 00:15:23,460
500 guan.

376
00:15:27,840 --> 00:15:30,840
My son was hired to be a music teacher.

377
00:15:31,080 --> 00:15:33,030
How come he's dead all of a sudden?

378
00:15:33,320 --> 00:15:34,110
I have said it.

379
00:15:34,110 --> 00:15:36,030
A medical emergency took Mr. Ji.

380
00:15:36,880 --> 00:15:38,520
He's so young.

381
00:15:38,520 --> 00:15:40,550
What medical emergency could he have?

382
00:15:40,640 --> 00:15:43,030
How did he become a pot of ash?

383
00:15:43,550 --> 00:15:44,520
Cut it down.

384
00:15:44,960 --> 00:15:46,230
You've got a lot of money.

385
00:15:46,230 --> 00:15:47,520
Take the urn and leave.

386
00:15:47,960 --> 00:15:49,670
What do I need the money for?

387
00:15:49,880 --> 00:15:51,760
I will have my explanation!

388
00:15:52,520 --> 00:15:53,550
You can't get in.

389
00:15:53,710 --> 00:15:54,640
Get her out of here!

390
00:15:54,640 --> 00:15:55,960
Let me in!

391
00:15:56,360 --> 00:15:58,050
[Back Door of Zhang's Mansion]
Let me in!

392
00:15:58,550 --> 00:16:00,230
Let me in!

393
00:16:00,400 --> 00:16:02,960
My poor boy!

394
00:16:03,740 --> 00:16:08,220
[Zhang's Mansion]

395
00:16:50,580 --> 00:16:53,860
[Warm Chamber of Zhang's Mansion]

396
00:16:54,640 --> 00:16:57,640
The sun lights up the Incense Burner Peak, creating a purple mist.

397
00:16:58,150 --> 00:17:02,640
Two golden orioles sing amid the emerald willows.

398
00:17:02,640 --> 00:17:06,710
Stopping my carriage, I admire the evening maple forest.

399
00:17:07,040 --> 00:17:12,800
I would rather be a pair of mandarin ducks than envy immortals.

400
00:17:13,040 --> 00:17:15,160
You are intruding,

401
00:17:15,710 --> 00:17:17,520
and it's not the conduct of a gentleman.

402
00:17:19,230 --> 00:17:20,040
Guards!

403
00:17:20,350 --> 00:17:21,040
Take him!

404
00:17:24,230 --> 00:17:25,070
Bring him over.

405
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:28,000
You treacherous man.

406
00:17:28,920 --> 00:17:29,920
What's your business up here?

407
00:17:30,110 --> 00:17:31,400
I saw you put out a bounty

408
00:17:31,400 --> 00:17:32,590
for the Hat Demon by the gate,

409
00:17:32,710 --> 00:17:33,800
and I'd like to be a part of the action.

410
00:17:33,800 --> 00:17:34,830
Oh, like you will!

411
00:17:35,110 --> 00:17:35,880
Get him out of here!

412
00:17:36,520 --> 00:17:37,400
Wait.

413
00:17:44,560 --> 00:17:46,680
Since you are already here,

414
00:17:47,160 --> 00:17:49,040
tell us

415
00:17:49,640 --> 00:17:51,760
about what you can do.

416
00:17:59,310 --> 00:18:01,040
So, you can't do anything.

417
00:18:02,400 --> 00:18:03,710
I've been to

418
00:18:04,040 --> 00:18:05,800
the crematorium in the suburb

419
00:18:05,800 --> 00:18:07,350
and witnessed cremation.

420
00:18:07,710 --> 00:18:09,160
I can never forget

421
00:18:09,400 --> 00:18:11,000
that smell.

422
00:18:11,190 --> 00:18:13,230
I smelled the same scent in the garden

423
00:18:14,400 --> 00:18:16,310
of Zhang's Mansion just now.

424
00:18:18,190 --> 00:18:20,640
It's the smell of a young

425
00:18:20,640 --> 00:18:22,190
and nice-looking man burnt.

426
00:18:22,710 --> 00:18:23,470
Total nonsense.

427
00:18:24,190 --> 00:18:25,800
Death must be what you are seeking here.

428
00:18:28,880 --> 00:18:31,040
You do have some tricks up your sleeves.

429
00:18:33,110 --> 00:18:34,920
How many bodies are cremated

430
00:18:34,920 --> 00:18:37,070
in the crematorium outside the city?

431
00:18:37,070 --> 00:18:39,400
I can't bear the thought

432
00:18:39,400 --> 00:18:41,830
of sending my man there and letting him share a place

433
00:18:42,400 --> 00:18:44,040
with so many people.

434
00:18:44,920 --> 00:18:48,350
I heard that some people buried bodies in the garden,

435
00:18:49,110 --> 00:18:50,880
and the plants

436
00:18:50,880 --> 00:18:52,880
all died overnight.

437
00:18:53,110 --> 00:18:54,520
Even the roots are rotten.

438
00:18:55,040 --> 00:18:56,880
Scaring warms crawling on the land.

439
00:18:57,470 --> 00:18:59,400
The smell is awful.

440
00:19:00,620 --> 00:19:02,170
Then, I realized

441
00:19:02,170 --> 00:19:03,900
that bury the ash

442
00:19:03,900 --> 00:19:05,260
from burning the body in the garden

443
00:19:05,900 --> 00:19:08,520
and the flowers grow better.

444
00:19:08,520 --> 00:19:10,920
The colors are brighter.

445
00:19:12,470 --> 00:19:15,310
Guess where that young man is right now?

446
00:19:25,590 --> 00:19:28,800
As it turned out, cremains are the best fertilizer.

447
00:19:30,070 --> 00:19:32,880
Look at how beautiful my flowers are.

448
00:19:35,160 --> 00:19:37,230
You intruded into my place.

449
00:19:37,230 --> 00:19:39,070
Do you want to become my fertilizer as well?

450
00:19:43,160 --> 00:19:45,680
I think that Lady Zhang's most urgent business

451
00:19:45,680 --> 00:19:47,830
is not the fertilizer,

452
00:19:47,950 --> 00:19:49,560
but the Hat Demon, right?

453
00:19:55,220 --> 00:19:56,690
Do you have what it takes?

454
00:20:02,310 --> 00:20:03,160
Lady Zhang.

455
00:20:03,880 --> 00:20:07,350
I'm Zhao Buyou, a former official at the Office of Justice.

456
00:20:07,470 --> 00:20:09,070
I helped the Kaifeng Prefecture with the investigation.

457
00:20:09,640 --> 00:20:10,880
I'm giving you the information

458
00:20:11,560 --> 00:20:12,800
just to prove

459
00:20:12,800 --> 00:20:14,880
that I am capable of working for you.

460
00:20:17,560 --> 00:20:18,640
Lady Zhang.

461
00:20:19,110 --> 00:20:20,400
Don't listen to his nonsense.

462
00:20:21,230 --> 00:20:22,110
If I can't do it,

463
00:20:22,830 --> 00:20:23,920
I…

464
00:20:23,920 --> 00:20:26,190
I can be your fertilizer.

465
00:20:27,710 --> 00:20:28,880
Okay.

466
00:20:30,110 --> 00:20:32,470
Let's see what you are made of.

467
00:20:42,400 --> 00:20:43,280
We are back.

468
00:20:44,880 --> 00:20:45,880
Welcome home.

469
00:20:48,520 --> 00:20:49,560
Wen Yue.

470
00:20:50,520 --> 00:20:51,800
Have you heard

471
00:20:51,800 --> 00:20:53,590
of the incident about the Hat Demon

472
00:20:53,590 --> 00:20:55,310
on Yanglou Street from last night?

473
00:20:56,190 --> 00:20:57,430
People are talking about it.

474
00:20:59,230 --> 00:21:00,160
Do you remember

475
00:21:00,470 --> 00:21:01,400
Mo'er was quite close to a friend

476
00:21:01,400 --> 00:21:03,470
when he was a child

477
00:21:03,470 --> 00:21:04,310
named Sun Bo.

478
00:21:05,640 --> 00:21:07,640
Of course. How can I forget?

479
00:21:07,950 --> 00:21:09,830
Mo'er doesn't have many friends.

480
00:21:10,070 --> 00:21:12,040
Sun Bo was the only one he was close to.

481
00:21:12,040 --> 00:21:13,000
That's him!

482
00:21:13,470 --> 00:21:14,520
He's in trouble.

483
00:21:15,000 --> 00:21:16,640
He's the suspect in the Hat Demon Case.

484
00:21:16,830 --> 00:21:18,640
The Kaifeng Prefecture arrested him.

485
00:21:20,430 --> 00:21:22,920
Didn't Sun Bo disappeared

486
00:21:23,310 --> 00:21:24,760
after a family accident?

487
00:21:24,760 --> 00:21:26,470
He did.

488
00:21:26,470 --> 00:21:28,310
But Mo'er and I met him again yesterday.

489
00:21:28,310 --> 00:21:30,470
I wonder if he has moved back.

490
00:21:31,070 --> 00:21:31,760
Wen Yue.

491
00:21:31,950 --> 00:21:34,560
We all thought that he was an honest man.

492
00:21:34,800 --> 00:21:37,280
He has helped everyone in the Yanglou Street neighborhood.

493
00:21:37,520 --> 00:21:39,350
They must have wronged him.

494
00:21:39,680 --> 00:21:40,880
Look at Mo'er.

495
00:21:41,160 --> 00:21:42,590
Staring into the void again.

496
00:21:44,280 --> 00:21:45,800
Buyou

497
00:21:45,950 --> 00:21:48,760
is familiar with Inspector Gu, right?

498
00:21:50,920 --> 00:21:52,190
Kind of.

499
00:21:52,230 --> 00:21:53,040
Why?

500
00:21:53,350 --> 00:21:54,830
We'd like to see

501
00:21:54,830 --> 00:21:57,040
if Buyou can talk to Inspector Gu

502
00:21:57,310 --> 00:21:59,160
and let us see Sun Bo.

503
00:21:59,280 --> 00:22:01,350
We just want to know what's the situation

504
00:22:01,350 --> 00:22:02,310
or what happened.

505
00:22:02,760 --> 00:22:03,560
When Buyou comes back,

506
00:22:03,560 --> 00:22:04,710
you can ask him yourself.

507
00:22:04,710 --> 00:22:07,190
Wen Yue, he listens to you.

508
00:22:08,560 --> 00:22:10,760
Can you ask him for us?

509
00:22:11,160 --> 00:22:11,950
All right.

510
00:22:11,950 --> 00:22:12,950
When Buyou comes back,

511
00:22:12,950 --> 00:22:14,160
I'll ask him.

512
00:22:14,310 --> 00:22:14,800
Great.

513
00:22:14,800 --> 00:22:16,760
You two should stop getting involved in things like this.

514
00:22:16,880 --> 00:22:19,160
You focus on your study in the clinic.

515
00:22:22,310 --> 00:22:23,470
Wen Yue.

516
00:22:23,470 --> 00:22:25,520
I haven't told you yet.

517
00:22:26,350 --> 00:22:28,160
The clinic fired me again.

518
00:22:28,520 --> 00:22:30,280
Again?

519
00:22:31,470 --> 00:22:33,110
What's the reason this time?

520
00:22:33,640 --> 00:22:36,040
I twisted someone's arm yesterday.

521
00:22:36,040 --> 00:22:37,430
You hurt someone?

522
00:22:40,160 --> 00:22:41,560
The dishes are delicious.

523
00:22:42,160 --> 00:22:43,310
Father insisted

524
00:22:43,310 --> 00:22:45,280
on playing cards at Xie Laoba's place.

525
00:22:45,280 --> 00:22:46,470
Wen Yue, let me tell you.

526
00:22:46,710 --> 00:22:49,310
When I went to the clinic to check on Ban'er…

527
00:22:49,310 --> 00:22:50,950
Although Physician Ge is well off,

528
00:22:50,950 --> 00:22:52,560
they don't have decent food there.

529
00:22:52,560 --> 00:22:54,760
The best dish is your cured meat.

530
00:22:56,960 --> 00:22:58,360
He spoke highly of you for your good performance.

531
00:22:58,360 --> 00:22:58,930
Zhao Buyou.

532
00:22:59,560 --> 00:23:00,400
Have you finished your food?

533
00:23:01,110 --> 00:23:02,070
Almost. Why?

534
00:23:02,560 --> 00:23:04,190
If you are done, come with me.

535
00:23:04,760 --> 00:23:06,110
All right. I'll do the dishes later.

536
00:23:06,640 --> 00:23:07,430
What is it?

537
00:23:07,950 --> 00:23:09,830
I didn't go to the clinic today.

538
00:23:18,710 --> 00:23:21,280
I want to visit Physician Ge tomorrow.

539
00:23:22,680 --> 00:23:24,160
Do you care

540
00:23:24,160 --> 00:23:25,400
about your brother and sister at all?

541
00:23:25,400 --> 00:23:27,470
Zhao Ban'er was fired by the clinic yesterday.

542
00:23:28,830 --> 00:23:29,560
How should I know?

543
00:23:29,560 --> 00:23:30,760
She didn't say anything.

544
00:23:32,470 --> 00:23:33,280
Ban'er!

545
00:23:34,830 --> 00:23:35,950
These two whelps.

546
00:23:35,950 --> 00:23:36,830
They run off.

547
00:23:37,710 --> 00:23:38,590
They left.

548
00:23:38,680 --> 00:23:39,800
She's worried that you may scold her.

549
00:23:40,310 --> 00:23:40,880
Oh, no!

550
00:23:41,160 --> 00:23:42,830
They've been talking about a case since they got back.

551
00:23:43,280 --> 00:23:44,230
I have to go after them.

552
00:23:51,760 --> 00:23:52,430
Where are they?

553
00:23:52,430 --> 00:23:54,230
[Opera Theater, Yanglou Street ]

554
00:23:54,230 --> 00:23:54,920
Yao He!

555
00:23:54,920 --> 00:23:55,710
- Over here. - Yao He.

556
00:23:58,310 --> 00:23:59,950
We almost got caught.

557
00:24:00,160 --> 00:24:01,560
It's fortunate that we were fast.

558
00:24:09,190 --> 00:24:11,310
I was so nervous at dinner

559
00:24:11,310 --> 00:24:12,400
that I'm hungry again.

560
00:24:12,800 --> 00:24:14,310
I'll go get you some food.

561
00:24:14,920 --> 00:24:15,800
Wait here.

562
00:24:15,800 --> 00:24:16,950
- Thank you. - Mo'er.

563
00:24:18,680 --> 00:24:20,190
What brought you here?

564
00:24:20,800 --> 00:24:22,070
I heard that

565
00:24:22,070 --> 00:24:24,920
there's a Hat Demon Hunting Assembly on the Yanglou Street.

566
00:24:24,920 --> 00:24:26,160
I'm here for that.

567
00:24:26,760 --> 00:24:27,800
There are a lot of people.

568
00:24:28,590 --> 00:24:29,710
Looks lively.

569
00:24:30,800 --> 00:24:32,070
