Did you ask for me?

866
00:40:29,310 --> 00:40:30,870
Let's talk somewhere else.

867
00:40:31,870 --> 00:40:32,440
Yes.

868
00:40:38,760 --> 00:40:40,680
Buyou boarded Zhang Qiniang's carriage.

