with a friend last night.

896
00:42:22,350 --> 00:42:23,440
We had a good chat

897
00:42:23,440 --> 00:42:25,070
and forgot about the time.

898
00:42:25,440 --> 00:42:26,550
Which friend?

899
00:42:26,960 --> 00:42:28,550
You'd forget about home for that friend?

900
00:42:29,070 --> 00:42:30,150
A new friend.

901
00:42:31,630 --> 00:42:34,150
I tried to leave a few times

902
00:42:34,350 --> 00:42:35,590
but I was stopped

903
00:42:35,590 --> 00:42:37,110
to chat for longer.

904
00:42:37,550 --> 00:42:38,390
Did you drink?

905
00:42:39,350 --> 00:42:40,520
Just a little.

906
00:42:42,720 --> 00:42:43,630
How's your health

907
00:42:43,630 --> 00:42:44,870
